Russia ' s Yeltsin to make radio address . President Boris Yeltsin , who is preparing for heart surgery , will make a radio address to the nation at 0700 GMT on Friday , a presidential spokesman said . The spokesman could not give any details about the contents of the president ' s address . Yeltsin , 65 , whose heart problems have kept him away from his Kremlin office since late June , has addressed the nation on key issues of domestic policy several times since his re - election in July . Yeltsin is currently in a sanatorium outside Moscow . 
